title: Dracula vs Frankenstein (Los monstruos del terror)

sources.title: Los monstruos del terror (1970)
sources.description: Aliens from a dying world plot to conquer earth by praying on man's superstitions. Bringing two dead scientists back to life, they use their knowledge to re-animate various earth monsters, including the werewolf, Frankenstein's monster, the mummy Tao-Tet, and the vampire Count de Meirhoff.
